   <body>
      <p>Press the<uicontrol> Section</uicontrol> button to show detailed information about the
         measurement data of a section. You can quickly change to another section by pressing the
         Section <uicontrol>arrow </uicontrol>buttons.</p>
      <p>Press on a bottle image to show only that bottle and related information. Press again on the bottle image to show all bottles again.  Press on a bottle to see more data about a specific cavity.</p>
      <p>
         <fig id="fig_jgy_prg_fdc">
            <image href="media/image1.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_kgy_prg_fdc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>
         <fig id="fig_ymg_srg_fdc">
            <image href="media/image2.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_zmg_srg_fdc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Press on a graph to zoom on the image. Press again on the graph to return to the normal view.</p>
      <p>
         <fig id="fig_jrb_trg_fdc">
            <image href="media/image3.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_krb_trg_fdc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Press on the up and down arrow keys to change the Region. Press on the arrow keys &lt; &gt; to go back and forward in time.</p>
      <p>Press the Squares Icon to expand the view and show the bottles above each other.</p>
      <p>
         <fig id="fig_sh1_vrg_fdc">
            <image href="media/image4.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_th1_vrg_fdc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Press the Filter Icon to filter the graph data. The screens below show no filter (left) and one filter (right).</p>
